Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.05,0:20:04.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur6}那個 各位我 請認真考慮一下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.35,0:20:07.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur6}就這樣 在激烈討論的最後
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.20,0:20:11.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur6}我們終於定下了書名
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.38,0:20:19.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur6}沙耶小姐 真可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.73,0:20:21.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur6}哈啦咻
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.82,0:20:26.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur6}今後你打算怎麼辦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.41,0:20:30.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur6}我打算去搶回我的頭髮
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.74,0:20:33.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur6}估計還黏在人偶的頭上
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.79,0:20:35.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur6}是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.08,0:20:38.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur6}嗯 不過犯人已經抓到了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.77,0:20:41.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur6}只要找到人偶就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.61,0:20:44.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur6}謝謝你 伊蕾娜小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.81,0:20:47.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur6}不用謝 伊蕾娜小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.10,0:20:49.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur6}晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.90,0:20:51.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur6}晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.21,0:21:08.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur6}咦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.29,0:21:12.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur6}是夢嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.31,0:21:29.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur6}好了 出發吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.81,0:21:34.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur6}好了 現在有個問題
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.34,0:21:37.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur6}穿行於清澈藍天之下
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.75,0:21:41.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur6}在場之人無不回眸凝視
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.63,0:21:44.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur6}失聲驚嘆於其美貌的魔女
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.99,0:21:46.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur6}究竟是誰呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.25,0:21:49.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur6}那是在旅途中
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.47,0:21:54.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur6}不斷編織著我和我們的故事《魔女之旅》的人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.41,0:21:57.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur6}沒錯 就是我
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.75,0:22:46.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur6}對…對不起 我太專注於寫字了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.22,0:22:51.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur6}不不 我才應該道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.06,0:22:57.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur6}不過 走路時還是要注意周圍
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.83,0:23:01.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur6}不然只會限制了自己的視野
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.77,0:23:03.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur6}對不起 謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.28,0:23:14.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur6}沒事 下次我們都注意些吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.06,0:23:16.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur6}好…好
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.04,0:23:41.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur6}那時我還不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.57,0:23:46.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur6}以後我會和她一起旅行
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.49,0:23:54.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur6}她的名字叫做艾姆妮西亞
